(25, 'PHOTO PUZZLE CHALLENGE', 'photo-puzzle-challenge', 'Get your photo taken, then race against the clock to solve your own face puzzle in just 2 minutes! A fast, fun, and interactive event challenge.', '<h3 data-start=\"194\" data-end=\"252\" class=\"\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\"><span data-start=\"198\" data-end=\"252\" style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Photo Puzzle Challenge – Snap, Shuffle &amp; Solve! 🧩</span></h3><p data-start=\"254\" data-end=\"648\" class=\"\">Bring a spark of fun and brainpower to your event with the Photo Puzzle Challenge! In this exciting activation, players first get their photo snapped by a webcam. Then the real challenge begins—a jumbled puzzle of their own face appears on screen, and they have just 2 minutes to solve it! It’s a race against time that’s perfect for corporate events, exhibitions, school activations, and more.</p><h4 data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"674\" class=\"\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\"><span data-start=\"655\" data-end=\"672\" style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">How It Works:</span></h4><p data-start=\"675\" data-end=\"849\" class=\"\">📸 A photo is taken live using a webcam.<br data-start=\"715\" data-end=\"718\">🧩 The photo is instantly turned into a shuffled puzzle.<br data-start=\"774\" data-end=\"777\">⏱️ Players have 120 seconds to solve it—beat the clock or lose the game!</p><h4 data-start=\"851\" data-end=\"900\" class=\"\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;