(30, 'NEON LIGHT PAINT BOOTH', 'neon-light-paint-booth', 'Custom neon designs for your event, with instant prints and sharing.', '<p data-start=\"369\" data-end=\"450\" style=\"text-align: justify; \"><strong data-start=\"374\" data-end=\"444\">Neon Light Paint Booth – Unleash Vibrant Creativity at Your Event!</strong>&nbsp;</p><p data-start=\"452\" data-end=\"914\" style=\"text-align: justify; \">Illuminate your event with the <strong data-start=\"483\" data-end=\"509\">Neon Light Paint Booth</strong>, where glowing neon lights create mesmerizing, colorful designs in every photo. Using <strong data-start=\"596\" data-end=\"623\">electrified glass tubes</strong> or bulbs filled with <strong data-start=\"645\" data-end=\"662\">rarefied neon</strong> gases, this interactive experience offers both <strong data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"727\">entertainment</strong> and <strong data-start=\"732\" data-end=\"752\">brand visibility</strong>. Guests will love the unique, vivid effects on their photos, and you’ll enjoy the endless <strong data-start=\"843\" data-end=\"869\">branding possibilities</strong> as their neon creations light up the room.</p><p data-start=\"916\" data-end=\"1280\"></p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong data-start=\"919\" data-end=\"961\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Why Choose the Neon Light Paint Booth?</strong></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"966\" data-end=\"997\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Stunning neon light effects</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> – Create glowing, artistic photos that pop</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1078\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Perfect for brand activations</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> – Customize the lighting and design to match&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span