(36, 'FLIP BOOK', 'flip-book', 'Turn guests\' videos into images, flip through them in an interactive flipbook.', '<p data-start=\"286\" data-end=\"353\" style=\"text-align: justify; \"><strong data-start=\"291\" data-end=\"346\">Flip Book – A Personalized, Interactive Experience!</strong>&nbsp;</p><p data-start=\"355\" data-end=\"658\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Make your event unforgettable with our <strong data-start=\"394\" data-end=\"407\">Flip Book</strong>! A short video clip is turned into a series of images that gradually change as guests flip through the book. It\'s an engaging and creative way to relive event moments, and it\'s fully customizable with a cover that matches your event theme or brand.</p><p data-start=\"660\" data-end=\"867\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">The <strong data-start=\"664\" data-end=\"677\">Flip Book</strong> offers a fun and interactive way to give guests a unique keepsake that they can cherish long after the event. Each flip brings a new image to life, capturing the excitement of the moment.</p><p data-start=\"869\" data-end=\"1102\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&nbsp;</span><strong data-start=\"872\" data-end=\"897\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Why Choose Flip Book?</strong></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"924\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Customizable cover</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> – Align with your event theme or brand.</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"969\" data-end=\"993\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Interactive keepsake</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> – A fun way to relive memories.</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"1030\" data-end=\"1044\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Engagement</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem