(43, 'MINI PHOTO BOOTH', 'mini-photo-boot', 'Display your logo on an LED TV with unlimited prints and custom overlays.', '<p data-start=\"405\" data-end=\"482\" style=\"text-align: justify; \">&nbsp;<strong data-start=\"409\" data-end=\"480\">Mini Photo Booth with LED TV – Compact, Customizable &amp; Captivating!</strong>&nbsp;</p><p data-start=\"484\" data-end=\"712\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Take your event to the next level with our <strong data-start=\"527\" data-end=\"559\">Mini Photo Booth with LED TV</strong>! No need for sticker branding—your event’s <strong data-start=\"603\" data-end=\"611\">logo</strong> or <strong data-start=\"615\" data-end=\"624\">theme</strong> is displayed seamlessly on the built-in LED TV, keeping things sleek and professional.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Enjoy the same amazing photo booth experience with </span><strong data-start=\"765\" data-end=\"791\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">unlimited photo prints</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> and </span><strong data-start=\"796\" data-end=\"821\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">personalized overlays</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> that reflect your unique branding. This compact solution delivers big impact, ensuring your event is both engaging and memorable.</span></p><p data-start=\"953\" data-end=\"1385\"></p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong data-start=\"956\" data-end=\"1004\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Why Choose the Mini Photo Booth with LED TV?</strong></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"1009\" data-end=\"1027\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Sleek branding</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> – Showcase your logo or theme directly on the LED TV.</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"1086\" data-end=\"1112\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Unlimited photo prints</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> – G