(46, 'INSTANT BOTTLE PRINTING', 'instant-bottle-printing', 'Guests customize bottles live—boosting engagement and brand visibility.', '<p data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"340\" style=\"text-align: justify; \"><strong data-start=\"256\" data-end=\"332\">Onsite Bottle Printing – A Unique Branding Experience!</strong>&nbsp;</p><p data-start=\"342\" data-end=\"661\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Turn ordinary bottles into personalized keepsakes with <strong data-start=\"397\" data-end=\"421\">live onsite printing</strong>! Guests can customize bottles with names, messages, or designs, creating a <strong data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"521\">memorable experience</strong> while showcasing your brand. This interactive activity boosts engagement and ensures your logo stays in their hands long after the event.</p><p data-start=\"663\" data-end=\"865\" style=\"text-align: justify; \"><strong data-start=\"666\" data-end=\"697\">Why Onsite Bottle Printing?</strong></p><p data-start=\"663\" data-end=\"865\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ Enhances brand visibility with a lasting impression</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ Engages guests with a fun, creative activity</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ Perfect for corporate events, activations, and giveaways</span></div></p><p data-start=\"867\" data-end=\"1023\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify; \">Let your brand flow with every sip—engage, personalize, and promote with <strong data-start=\"940\" data-end=\"966\">Onsite Bottle Printing</strong>!&nbsp;</p>', 1, 'bottle-print-bottle-printing.png', '\"[null]\"', '[\"bottleprinting1-67f3a422ec69d.jpg-instant-bottle-printing.jpg\",\"bottleprinting2-67f3a423b74c6.jpg-instant-bottle-printing.jpg\",\"bottleprinting3-67f3a42894c6a.jpg-instant-bottle-printing.jpg\",\"bottleprinting4-67f3a428d088b.jpg-instant-bottle-pri