(67, 'SPIN ART BIKE', 'spin-art-bike', 'Pedal your way to a masterpiece! The Spin Art Bike combines fun, fitness, and creativity to create vibrant art at your event.', '<p data-start=\"117\" data-end=\"483\" class=\"\"><strong data-start=\"117\" data-end=\"169\">Spin Art Bike – Pedal Your Way to a Masterpiece!</strong><br data-start=\"169\" data-end=\"172\">\r\nAdd a creative twist to your event with the Spin Art Bike! Guests hop on the bike, pedal to create colorful artwork, and watch their unique masterpieces come to life in real-time. This interactive activity combines fun and fitness, making it perfect for brand activations, corporate events, festivals, and more.</p><h4 data-start=\"485\" data-end=\"509\" class=\"\"><strong data-start=\"490\" data-end=\"507\">How It Works:</strong></h4><p data-start=\"510\" data-end=\"729\" class=\"\">🚴‍♂️ Guests pedal the bike to power a spinning art canvas.<br data-start=\"569\" data-end=\"572\">\r\n🎨 As they pedal, vibrant paints are splashed to create beautiful, one-of-a-kind art pieces.<br data-start=\"664\" data-end=\"667\">\r\n🏆 The result? A masterpiece they can take home as a souvenir!</p><h4 data-start=\"731\" data-end=\"771\" class=\"\"><strong data-start=\"736\" data-end=\"769\">Why Choose the Spin Art Bike?</strong></h4><p data-start=\"772\" data-end=\"1069\" class=\"\">✅ Fun &amp; Interactive – Pedal-powered artwork is engaging for all ages!<br data-start=\"841\" data-end=\"844\">\r\n✅ Customizable – Add your logo or branding to the art canvas.<br data-start=\"905\" data-end=\"908\">\r\n✅ Creative &amp; Memorable – Guests create their own unique art pieces.<br data-start=\"975\" data-end=\"978\">\r\n✅ Perfect for All Events – Ideal for festivals, trade shows, corporate events, and parties.</p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p data-start=\"1071\" data-end=\"1218\" class=\"\">Now available for rentals in Dubai &amp; Abu Dhabi, the Spin Art Bike adds creativity and fun to any event, leaving guests with a memorable experience!</p>', 1, 'spin art bike-67f640d5d9002.png-spin-art-bike.png', '\"[null]\"', '[\"spinartbike2-67f640dbef31c.jpg-spin-art-bike.jpg\",\"spinartbike1-67f640dc3559d.jpg-spin-art-bike.jpg\",\"spinartbike4-67f640e35ef3d.jpg-spin-art-bike.jpg\",\"spinartbike3-67f640e3b521f.jpg-spin-art-bike.jpg\",\"spinartbike5-67f640e79a21f.jpg-spin-art-bike.jpg\"]', NULL, 2, '2025-04-09 16:42:00', '2025-04-12 17:51:36', 'Spin Art Bike – Pedal Powered Creativity | MIRROR BOOTH EVENT SERVICES L.L.C', 'Pedal the Spin Art Bike to create unique art at your event! A fun and interactive activity that lets guests make colorful masterpieces.', 'spin art bike, interactive art, event creativity, pedal-powered art, unique event activity, Dubai event fun, art activation, branded art canvas', 'Guest pedaling the Spin Art Bike to create colorful artwork at an event, with vibrant paints splashing onto the spinning canvas.'),
